				<source type="string">Gnoll</source>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>Although not, strictly speaking, different races, gnolls from the civilized lands live in an environment so different than their savage brethren that they are considered separate subraces. Choose one of them.</p>
					<linklist>
						<link class="reference_subrace" recordname="race.id-00003.subraces.id-00001@Southlands Heroes">Civilized Gnolls</link>
						<link class="reference_subrace" recordname="race.id-00003.subraces.id-00002@Southlands Heroes">Savage Gnolls</link>
					</linklist>
				</text>
				<type type="string">racial</type>
			</id-00003>
